    "description": "杰玛·麦克谢一次又一次地带来了惊喜，这个最新的Weapon Pack也不例外。总共有3种全新的武器，每一种都有自己的特点，包括模组和专属套组。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Deimos霰弹枪对于任何霰弹枪爱好者来说都是非常通用的选择。Deimos允许你在高伤害泵动形态和高射速自动形态之间进行选择。<br>Deimos有9种独特模组以及1件专属套组。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353510/extras/6d634e6775846084fc75f636a6ac66cb.poster.avif?t=1756108638\" width=600 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353510/extras/6d634e6775846084fc75f636a6ac66cb.webm?t=1756108638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353510/extras/6d634e6775846084fc75f636a6ac66cb.mp4?t=1756108638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Amaroq 900是一支擅长远距离射击的高伤害狙击步枪，以所有游戏中最著名的狙击步枪之一为模型。<br>Amaroq 900肯定会让你成为战场上的恐怖分子，它有12种独特模组，1种狙击步枪通用模组以及2件专属套组。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353510/extras/c60dcd5158e9204190a68dd96596c526.poster.avif?t=1756108638\" width=600 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353510/extras/c60dcd5158e9204190a68dd96596c526.webm?t=1756108638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353510/extras/c60dcd5158e9204190a68dd96596c526.mp4?t=1756108638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Campbell 74轻机枪能够将大量的火力投入到射程内，货真价实如假包换！它不仅有恐怖的射速，而且还配备了真正的枪管下挂火焰喷射器！ <br>Campbell 74有7种独特模组以及1件专属套组。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353510/extras/f2ad5fce8aa41e7e4320deadcf17fab6.poster.avif?t=1756108638\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353510/extras/f2ad5fce8aa41e7e4320deadcf17fab6.webm?t=1756108638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353510/extras/f2ad5fce8aa41e7e4320deadcf17fab6.mp4?t=1756108638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
